 important to do whatever you can to improve your credit rating before attempting to get a refinancing loan. Nevertheless, BD Nationwide Mortgage should provide some information about cost so that applicants can have an idea of what to expect.","The only way to get in touch with BD Nationwide is via phone and email. There are no frequently asked questions, no blogs and no online chat."]},"id":"712a0fdc-d6eb-4002-8a81-2d834065b6c5","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"6a1f210e-0781-4e5a-a1bd-25c2449d7df1","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["BD Nationwide Mortgage offers a variety of refinancing types.  It’s difficult to tell by visiting the website whether it stands out from the crowd in prices, features or service and support because there is no information regarding these things.  It’s obvious that it is limited when it comes to contact methods and applicants are likely to move on to the next company when they can’t get an idea of how much they’re going to pay for the service."]},"id":"3f502c5b-7bb1-4aa4-beae-5eb2cade3405","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_48672","url":"/nationwide-mortgage-loans-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"sabrina-rojas-weiss","url":"/author/sabrina-rojas-weiss","dateCreated":"2019-04-05T12:55:59Z","name":"Sabrina Rojas Weiss","dateModified":"2019-04-05T12:55:59Z","id":"tVZv6ejiouijuHU3n7n49Y","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2010-01-31T21:04:05Z","datePublished":"2010-01-31T21:04:05Z","name":"BD Nationwide Mortgage","synopsis":"Editor's Note: This review has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it no longer ranks as a top 10 product. The original review is below, but check out our current top 10 about Mortgage and Refinance here.","review":{"rating":63,"verdict":"BD Nationwide Mortgage provides many useful loan types and financing options. ","pros":["BD Nationwide Mortgage explains FHA loans in more detail th